def last_search_query(custom_controller_name = nil) name = (custom_controller_name || controller_name).to_s session[:last_search_queries][name] rescue nil end
def index_path_with_last_search_query(custom_query = {}) if last_search_query(custom_query[:controller]) url_for( { action: :index }. merge(custom_query). merge(last_search_query(custom_query[:controller])) ) else url_for(action: :index) end end
